QuestData.Title: Trappings of Success
QuestData.Description:
The wildlife of Zereth Mortis are attracted to the frenetic creation energy that flows throughout the land. When the wildlife finds something charged with that energy... they eat it!
The Mawsworn Cryptoseers have become aware of this and are attempting to find such wildlife to extract any remnants of that energy.
Eliminate the Cryptoseers, and use the Containment Trap to subdue and examine the wildlife for our research.
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay $1oa Mawsworn Cryptoseers and examine the wildlife listed.
QuestData.RewardText: This information will help us continue to unravel the mysteries of Zereth Mortis.
